rows.label: qst702607_msg0001
rows.name:
Dudan salvaged the Fortune-
Findermatron 4000 for me.

rows.label: qst702607_msg0002
rows.name:
It looked just like a gold-gathering
machine I saw in a picture book
once when I was a little girl.

rows.label: qst702607_msg0003
rows.name: I knew that it must be a sign.

rows.label: qst702607_msg0004
rows.name:
Dudan really tried hard, but in the end
he's no engineering expert. I think he's
pretty much done as much as he can.

rows.label: qst702607_msg0005
rows.name:
Would you be able to take the machine
to someone who knows what they're
doing and get it fixed?

rows.label: qst702607_msg0006
rows.name:
I came all the way out here, and
I refuse to go back empty-handed.

rows.label: qst702607_msg0101
rows.name:
It got something! Did you see?
It got something!

rows.label: qst702607_msg0102
rows.name:
I really want to believe that it's
brought back some gold, but I
don't want to jinx it.

rows.label: qst702607_msg0103
rows.name: Could you check? I can't look!
